           <<hash(disclosure), hash(sensitiveData)>, signature>)
     )
     ]
    variants (modulo AC)
    1. disclosure
             = disclosure.24
       pkI   = pkI.26
       sensitiveData
             = sensitiveData.27
       signature
             = signature.29
       z     = checksign(signature.29,
